185. Telegram From the Department of State to the Embassy in RomaniaSource: Department of State, Records
                        from Ambassador Thomas W. Simons,
                        Jr., Lot 03 D 256, Chron December 1988. Confidential; Priority; Exdis. Sent
                        for information to Vienna for the delegation to the CSCE. Drafted by Becker; cleared by Seymour, Deal,
                            Simons, T.J. Rose (D), James
                        Collins (S/S), and D. Trotter (S/S–O); and approved by Whitehead.
